   835→              className="w-full p-2 bg-surface-light dark:bg-surface-dark border border-border-light dark:border-border-dark rounded-lg text-sm text-text-light-primary dark:text-text-dark-primary focus:ring-2 focus:ring-accent-blue outline-none"
   836→            >
